OL,3,CPlan to divert millions of patients
OL,4,Cfrom waiting lists with GP service
OL,5,Cexpansion
OL,7,FThe Government has set out plans to
OL,8,Fdivert up to two million patients from
OL,9,FNHS waiting lists by the end of next
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FA scheme which allows family doctors
OL,13,Fto seek advice from specialists before
OL,14,Freferring patients will be expanded
OL,15,Fwith the support of an #80 million
OL,16,Ffunding package.
OL,18,FMinisters said the move will "stop
OL,19,Fmasses of people" going to hospital
OL,20,Ffor "unnecessary appointments".
