OL,3,CPlan to divert millions of patients
OL,4,Cfrom waiting lists with GP service
OL,5,Cexpansion
OL,7,FThose benefiting include women with
OL,8,Fsymptoms of the menopause and patients
OL,9,Fwith ear, throat and nose issues,
OL,10,Faccording to the Department of Health
OL,11,Fand Social Care.
OL,13,FGPs welcomed the announcement but said
OL,14,Fthe scheme must be properly resourced.
OL,16,FThe initiative, known as advice and
OL,17,Fguidance, allows GPs to seek advice
OL,18,Ffrom specialists on the phone or
OL,19,Fonline before making a referral, to
OL,20,Fensure care is given in the most
OL,21,Fappropriate setting.
