OL,3,CPlan to divert millions of patients
OL,4,Cfrom waiting lists with GP service
OL,5,Cexpansion
OL,7,FIt can mean patients are referred for
OL,8,Fblood tests and scans from their
OL,9,Fsurgery, or directed to other
OL,10,Fcommunity services, for the likes of
OL,11,Fphysio, rather than being added to NHS
OL,12,Fwaiting lists.
OL,14,FUnder plans from the Department of
OL,15,FHealth and Social Care, the scheme
OL,16,Fwill be expanded with the aim of
OL,17,Fdiverting up to two million patients
OL,18,Fby the end of 2025/26.
