OL,4,Cfrom waiting lists with GP service
OL,5,Cexpansion
OL,7,FFrom this month, GP practices can now
OL,8,Fclaim for every request raised through
OL,9,Fadvice and guidance.
OL,11,FThe expansion will also aim to
OL,12,Fstandardise its use across the country.
OL,14,FIt follows an announcement in January
OL,15,Fthat GPs would be offered #20 every
OL,16,Ftime they consult a specialist using
OL,17,Fthe scheme.
