OL,7,FHealth minister Karin Smyth said: "By
OL,8,Fcaring for patients closer to home, we
OL,9,Fsave time and stop masses of people
OL,10,Fhaving to head to hospital for
OL,11,Funnecessary appointments in the first
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,F"We are rewiring the NHS so that we
OL,15,Fare doing things differently, more
OL,16,Fefficiently and delivering better
OL,17,Foutcomes for patients.
