OL,7,F"This scheme is a perfect example of
OL,8,Fhow we are saving patients time and
OL,9,Freducing pressure on key NHS services
OL,10,Fin the process."
OL,12,FAdvice and guidance has been used
OL,13,Fsince 2015, and the pathway was
OL,14,Fformalised by NHS England in 2021.
OL,16,FAccording to DHSC, between July and
OL,17,FDecember last year about 660,000
OL,18,Ftreatments were diverted from
OL,19,Fhospitals to the community as a result
OL,20,Fof the advice and guidance scheme, up
OL,21,F60,000 for the same period in 2023.
