OL,7,FProfessor Sir Sam Everington, who has
OL,8,Fbeen a GP in Tower Hamlets, east
OL,9,FLondon, since 1989, added: "Advice and
OL,10,Fguidance enables patients and GPs to
OL,11,Fget advice direct from a specialist,
OL,12,Ftypically within a week for routine
OL,13,Fcases.
OL,15,F"This means that patients get their
OL,16,Fhealth problems sorted rapidly,
OL,17,Fpreventing health deterioration and
OL,18,Favoiding long waits to be seen.
