OL,7,FProfessor Kamila Hawthorne, chairwoman
OL,8,Fof the Royal College of GPs, said:
OL,9,F"Advice and guidance services have the
OL,10,Fpotential to support GPs to refer
OL,11,Fappropriately and deliver care to
OL,12,Fpatients whilst they are waiting for
OL,13,Fspecialist treatment, but it's crucial
OL,14,Fthat GP services have the capacity to
OL,15,Faccommodate the shift from hospitals
OL,16,Fto community care so this funding is a
OL,17,Fgood step in the right direction.
