OL,7,F"In the past, some GPs have reported
OL,8,Fissues with using A&G services,
OL,9,Fincluding that they shift care into
OL,10,Fgeneral practice without appropriate
OL,11,Fresource, and that they can be used to
OL,12,Freject necessary referrals.
OL,14,F"We have always been supportive of the
OL,15,FGovernment's aspiration to shift more
OL,16,Fcare into the community, and an
OL,17,Fincreasing use of A&G services may
OL,18,Fhelp enable this, as long as it is
OL,19,Fproperly resourced across the country.
